{"word":"πληγή","slug":"πληγή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πληγή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πλήσσω\">πλήσσω</a></el>] ‘physical damage inflicted by forceful application’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> blow,</b> administered by thugs <b><a href='B:490 10:30'>Lk 10:30</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a punitive strike or blow, <b>stroke <a href='B:490 12:48'>Lk 12:48</a>; <a href='B:510 16:23'>Ac 16:23</a>; <a href='B:540 6:5'>2 Cor 6:5</a>; <a href='B:540 11:23'>11:23</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> wound <a href='B:510 16:33'>Ac 16:33</a>; <a href='B:730 13:3'>Rv 13:3</a>, <a href='B:730 13:12'>12</a>, <a href='B:730 13:14'>14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>d.</pp></b> of a major calamity, <b>plague <a href='B:730 9:18'>Rv 9:18</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πλέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πλῆθος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}